summary: A small starting player abode just outside the North gates to Riften.
descriptionHtml:
[center][heading][b][size=14][color=#3174d2]Hole in the Wall -Riften[/color][/size][/b][/heading]
[img]http://i1079.photobucket.com/albums/w503/ytnam/Skyrim/Hole%20in%20the%20Wall%20-%20Riften/Exterior.jpg[/img][/center]
A player room with a small amount of storage and an alchemist's table, just outside the North gate to Riften.
Designed for starting new characters, just a small base until you find your feet.
Minimal storage (all safe) and alchemy, with a campfire and cooking available just outside.
All smithing stations and wood chopping available just inside the gates!
Free Riften guards!
